title: Q Blockchain DAO
description: Q is a decentralized governance system that aims to democratize access to international private law and ensure fair dispute resolution in the decentralized world.

title: DeFi Governance
description: A decentralized organization focused on governing decentralized finance protocols and projects. By leveraging the collective wisdom and expertise of its members, the DAO aims to improve the security, efficiency, and transparency of DeFi platforms. It also serves as a platform for discussing and proposing changes to DeFi protocols.

title: Climate Solutions
description: A DAO dedicated to funding and promoting environmentally-friendly projects and technologies. Members pool resources to fund research and development, as well as initiatives focused on sustainable agriculture, renewable energy, and carbon reduction. The DAO also provides a platform for educating the public and advocating for climate-friendly policies.
